CatDescriptText: Related image and article published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, June 13, 1959, A16 reads: "Anyone For Dimples? - Gloria Sweeney shows her dimples as she models a hat and dress for the D.I. show."
TitMainTitle: Gloria Sweeney wearing light colored short sleeve dress with wide belt, light colored hand gloves, and light colored wide brim hat with ribbon, standing on runway with shell patterned carpet in Press Club of the Hotel Sherwyn for D.I. Club's "Atlantic City U.S.A"
